              "Actions": [
                {
                  "Type": "SpawnParticles",
                  "Offset": [ 0, 1.2, 0 ],
                  "ParticleSystem": "Explosion_Medium"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "$Comment": "Relentless Seek fallback: when not mid-charge (out of charge range, post-charge rest, or an obstructed charge) keep closing on the target. Same de-leashed pursuit as the Stalker so the Lunger never gives up.",
              "Reference": "Component_Instruction_Intelligent_Chase",
